milestones.description: Fletcher has become the top scorer in ODIs with 599 runs, going past Dennis Amiss's 509
Fletcher has scored 5 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, breaking Ian Chappell's record
Chris Old has broken the record for most sixes (6) in ODIs, going past Ian Chappell's 5
Dayle Hadlee and McKechnie's 48-run partnership is the highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 35 between Geoff Arnold and Fletcher
Fletcher has become the top scorer for ENG in ODIs with 599 runs, going past Dennis Amiss's 509
This is the highest match aggregate (452) involving teams England & New Zealand in ODIs
Hastings has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (9) for NZ, going past Glenn Turner
Fletcher and Chris Old's 66-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 42 between Alan Knott and Tony Greig
John Morrison and Barry Hadlee's 53-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 52 between Glenn Turner and Geoff Howarth
Dayle Hadlee and McKechnie's 48-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 25 between Bruce Taylor and Hadlee
